<div class="about-us-card">
    <div class="about-us-card-content">
        <h2 class="about-us-title">About Us</h2>
        <p>
            At <strong>Pet Adoption Welfare System (PAWS)</strong>, our mission is simple yet profound: to create a world where every animal has a loving home and every pet owner feels supported. We are a dedicated team of animal lovers, advocates, and community members working tirelessly to rescue, rehabilitate, and rehome stray and abandoned animals.
        </p>
        <p>
            Founded on the belief that every pet deserves a second chance, we partner with local shelters and passionate volunteers to provide comprehensive care for animals in need. Beyond adoption, we offer valuable resources, education, and services to help pet owners in our community thrive.
        </p>
        <p>
            Whether you’re looking to adopt a furry friend, contribute to our cause, or simply learn more about responsible pet care, we are here to guide you every step of the way. Together, we can build a community where compassion for animals knows no bounds.
        </p>
        <p>
            Welcome to <strong>Pet Adoption Welfare System (PAWS)</strong>—your partner in creating a better life for animals and the people who love them.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

